HotelRevAI - AI-Driven Revenue Analysis for Hotels
HotelRevAI is a Power BI-based analytics dashboard that transforms raw hotel booking data into actionable revenue insights. Built by Infosys Springboard Batch 13 Group 2 Team A, it analyzes 3 years of historical data to optimize RevPAR, ADR, and occupancy while reducing cancellations through AI-driven Key Influencers and predictive analytics. Features 5 interactive dashboards covering Revenue Performance, Customer Segmentation, Operational Efficiency, Cancellation Intelligence, and overall performance.

